                     <interp inst="t17891209-119-off564" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17891209-119-off564" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17891209-119-cd565" type="crimeDate">2d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-119-off564 t17891209-119-cd565"></join>, in the parish of St. Mary-le-bone, a pair of corderoy breeches, value 4 s. a pair of leather half boots, value 12 s. a pair of knee buckles, value 2 d. two shillings, a sixpence, and twelve halfpence in money
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17891209-119-victim1082" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hardy
                  <interp inst="t17891209-119-victim1082" type="surname" value="Hardy"></interp>
