                     <interp inst="t17891209-119-person1085" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             came to me to work, as usual, on Monday morning, and told me what he had lost, and that he had a suspicion of the man that slept with him: on the first day of this month I saw the prisoner coming for a waggon load of bricks, at the buildings where 
               <persName id="t17891209-119-person1086">
                  John
                   Hardy
               <interp inst="t17891209-119-person1086" type="surname" value="Hardy"></interp>
